OL,3,CHotel owner on 'crippling' reality of
OL,4,Ctrying to survive in cost of living
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,F"It's crippling us, and whether or not
OL,8,Fwe survive it is another matter," she
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,F"You used to get people for a week at
OL,12,Fa time, and that doesn't happen now.
OL,13,FIt's a lot of one nighters, a lot of
OL,14,Fshort breaks, not many people that
OL,15,Fcome for a whole week at a time. It
OL,16,Fhas changed a lot."
OL,18,FStephen Furness, who runs the Belgrave
OL,19,FSands Hotel, says he has been
OL,20,Fploughing money into the business but
OL,21,Fis seeing dwindling returns.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
