OL,3,CHotel owner on 'crippling' reality of
OL,4,Ctrying to survive in cost of living
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,F"If we keep going as we are, putting
OL,8,Four savings in to keep everything
OL,9,Fgoing, there's only so long your
OL,10,Fsavings will last," he said
OL,12,F"Everyone is worried. We look good,
OL,13,Fbut the net profit is not good. We've
OL,14,Fgot a lot of good operators that are
OL,15,Ftrying very hard, so let's hope it
OL,16,Fwill all come back."
