OL,3,CHotel owner on 'crippling' reality of
OL,4,Ctrying to survive in cost of living
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FAnd it's not just hotels that are
OL,8,Ffeeling the squeeze. Restaurants and
OL,9,Fcafe owners like Denise Darby at the
OL,10,FCafe Del Mar say fewer people are able
OL,11,Fto treat themselves.
OL,13,F"We're not as busy as we were before
OL,14,Flockdown, and I do know a lot of
OL,15,Fpeople who don't go out to eat because
OL,16,Fthey can't afford to anymore," Denise
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,19,F"So we're not making a lot of money,
OL,20,Fif anything just breaking even really."
